  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Endosonographically suspicous gastric subepithelial mass &lt;=3 cm.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  American Society of Anesthesiologists (ASA) classes IV or V

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Bleeding disorders

          -  Contraindications for endoscopy

          -  Endosonographically shown large vessels in the area for resection
